706750f-b.title: Brooklyn: Shore Boulevard - Beaumont Street
706750f-b.text:
Shore Boulevard (left), west from near Beaumont Street and viewing across Sheepshead Bay. Thekpiles mark the limit of the new waterfront bulkhead which is being erected by the W. P. A. in cojunction with the widening of the thoroughfare an additional twenty feet. Shore 'olevard is also visible in the background (trees thereon), where
it forms a right amgle at West Nnd Avenue.
View 1: June 24, 1936
View 2: July 7, 1936
View 3: September 11, 1936
Works Progress Administration
Five Boroughs Project
